Isabel Hodgins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isabel_Hodgins 0 Isabel Victoria Hodgins (born 23 November 1993) is an English actress. She is best known for portraying the current character, Victoria Sugden, in the ITV soap opera Emmerdale, since 2006. The character of Victoria was born in 1994 and has remained in the show ever since. Hodgins took over the role after producers decided to recast it, when the character was 12 years old.
